reviewText: The information to back up Elvis Alive is in fact, there but the production team overloaded this video with too many snips & video of various Elvis interviews. The best program regarding the Elvis I s story was the one done with the late, great Bill Bixby (The Incredible Hulk, The Courtship of Eddie's Father).  Mr Bixby appeared in a few of Elvis's Hal Wallis produced movies (the mix to late 60s cream cheese ones) but great family movies; being rated G and "clean", almost old Disney-like (think the original Love Bug, Ghost & Mr. Chicken, original Shaggy Dog).
My wife enjoyed this movie very much.
Good but documentary not long enough
This exact same video is already posted on You Tube.  Same exact information, so this is nothing new to anyone who has researched Elvis on You Tube!  Don't waste your money.
Do people really believe Elvis Presley is still alive? It's a stretch to believe this, but what do I know?

I thought this was great. I don't believe this because i'm a fan , people always put Elvis way up there ,he had a personal life too,We don't know what these people do on their own time , I'm sure he had  other intrests,and dreams he wanted to fulfill , Like John Travolta being a commerial airline pilot,who wudda thunk it. The facts in this film are overwhelming.
This is worth watching. There is a mystery that surrounds Elvis Presley's death. All Elvis fans should watch this.
